transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, thanks for calling Viagra. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hey, yeah, my name is Michael Wilson. I had ordered some Viagra from you, and you shipped me again and billed me again. You got me on some kind of subscription or something?

Speaker 1: Let me see what's going on here, Mr. Wilson. How are you today?

Speaker 2: I'm well, thanks for asking.

Speaker 1: Oh, you know what? It looks like they sent you out that replacement order, and yeah, you got set up on our VIP prescription to receive refill orders.

Speaker 2: Did you need that order? Did you want it? Did you even like the pills?

Speaker 1: Uh, you know what? I hadn't even tried the pills.

Speaker 2: I mean, um, yeah, so absolutely. I can definitely pause this for you, and you can have time to grabâ€”

Speaker 1: Yeah, pause it for me.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, so this definitely won't happen again. So just let us know how it goes. Once you get to try them out,

Speaker 1: you'll have the account all paused up, Mr. Wilson, and you'll be set.

Speaker 2: Okay, you have a great day.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: You too. Bye-bye now.

Speaker 1: All right. Take care. Bye-bye.
